    {
      "contentFieldValue": {
        "data": "<h2>Bug</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<span>Instead of </span><tt>webserver-${LCP_PROJECT_ID}.${LCP_SERVICE_DOMAIN</tt><span>}, u</span>se $http_host in default log config instead of building the prefix with environment variables</li>\n<li>Fixed autoscale alerts being created without service scaled</li>\n<li>Fixed CI startup process slow due to chown of the mounted volume</li>\n<li>Need to clean deployments when deleting projects</li>\n<li>Fixed DNS flap, HAProxy 503 error on backends</li>\n<li>Fixed switch state when moving between tabs</li>\n</ul>"
      },
